                    "SS2_ITEM_SANTAHAT_PICKUP":  "Â¡Te tengo!",
                    "SS2_ITEM_GREENCHOCOLATE_DESC":  "Al ser daÃ±ado por \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003e20%\u003c/style\u003e de tus PS totales o mÃ¡s, gana una gain a stacking buff that grants \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e50%\u003c/style\u003e base damage and \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e20%\u003c/style\u003e critical chance for \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e15s\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+5s per stack)\u003c/style\u003e. Damage in excess of the 20% max HP threshold is reduced by \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e50%\u003c/style\u003e.",
